      section.covid
        h1.covid__title Your health during these times.
        p.covid__tagline With a global pandemic that has taken the lives of so many people it's very important to stay safe during this craze. Learn more about how our company managed to make everyone's health a priority during a very difficult time in many people's lives.
        button.covid__cta Covid-19 crisis

